      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single offset distance (50 mm) per ASTM F1717 standard configuration. While this is the standard regulatory configuration, it represents only one loading condition. A second offset or loading angle was not tested, limiting the breadth of condition coverage. Achieved level 2 is below required level 3; this gap is acknowledged as a limitation of the current submission."
